en_814764_0	Directorate of Psychological Operations at the request of the Centre for Army Vocational Training (CAVT) at Saliyawewa organized a special lecture on ‘Propagation of Military Literature’ at the CAVT auditorium on Sunday (8).
en_814764_1	Major Sugath Chaminda of the Directorate of Psychological Operations delivered the lecture for the benefit of novice recruits under training at the CAVT.
en_814764_2	Senior military Officers including Brigadier W.M.R.J.K Senarathna, Commandant CAVT, staff Officers and Other Ranks listened to the lecture.
